verifier.value

Class Reduction

  • java.lang.Object
    • verifier.value.Value
      • verifier.value.Reduction

  • public class Reduction
extends Value
    The verifier will evaluate an AST to a reduction if there isn't enough information to evaluate what the rule asks for. The wrapped AST is a simpler problem than was given (a reduction).
